Figure 8. (a) CBOs and (b) VBOs as functions of the Ge/(Ge + Sn) ratio (

 x

) below 0.4; (●) and (○) indicate stoichiometric and off-stoichiometric CZTGSe with Cu/(Zn + Sn + Ge) ratios of ∼1 and ∼0.8, respectively.

Figure 10. (a) Average core-level shifts upon laser irradiation relative to those under dark condition for CZTGSe with Ge compositions (

 x

